description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 71, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 213, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Nine Lives for East, 2 for South, and Stringalong for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [213 Votes, Top 5% Score]
